When airlines have promotions, it's best to get clicking as quickly as possible. The FlySafair's X-Mas in July promotion is in full swing on their website and you've only got a few more hours to get that discount. It's a one-day-only chance to book a flight for travel up until the end of April 2020 and get up to 30 percent for a flight. There a few terms and conditions to keep in mind before you click and fly:   As is the case with online promotions such as this one, there will always be glitches and FlySafair has asked people to please bear this in mind.         